(83, 'widget_text', 'a:4:{i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:821:"If you are unable to adopt a greyhound but would still like to help, you can also sponsor one of our long-term residents. \r\n\r\nSome of the dogs at Greyhound Rescue are not suitable for re-homing under our Adoption Scheme. So therefore we have implemented a Sponsorship Scheme whereby anyone interested may Sponsor one of our Long Term Residents.\r\n\r\nFor a Fee of £25 a year you will receive a colour Photograph of your chosen Greyhound, a decorative certificate suitable for displaying, as well as letter from your chosen dog giving a brief history of their life.\r\n\r\nPlease contact us for further information to: dawn@greyhoundrescue.org.uk  \r\n\r\nPlease also be aware that we also accept (gratefully received) donations via paypal. You can use your credit or debit card to donate. See the bottom of the page for details. \r\n";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:6;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:3:"Who";s:4:"text";s:93:"Greyhound Rescue North Yorkshire now covers East Lincolnshire. <h4>Call Us\r\n01205 290145</h4>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:7;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:14:"[showbiz shop]";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
