(1, 2, '2013-06-02 18:24:56', '2013-06-02 17:24:56', '<a href="http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/dukey1.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-82" style="border: 1px solid black; margin: 10px;" src="http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/dukey1.jpg" alt="dukey" width="269" height="146" /></a>On 25th August 2013 we are doing a calendar photoshoot for our 2014 Greyhound Rescue calendar in aid of ''The Rescue Duke Appeal''!\r\nThanks to the boys at Kennings Building Supplies Ltd/eDecks &amp; some local girls who have kindly donated their bodies to raise money and awareness for our charity.\r\nWe would like to thank Kennings Building Supplies Ltd/eDecks staff who are taking part in the calendar and Nigel and Michaela Kenning for the use of a few tools.\r\nNo way to talk about their staff I know but I am sure it will be a lot of fun and I can confirm that Karen Schultz, much to her horror is also appearing in the calendar and I can assure you, she will be removing some items of clothing. However, I have been told she would have to have her wellies surgically removed so due to timescales, they may have to stay on!\r\nPlease watch out for more updates on the calendar in the next few days.\r\n\r\nThe Calendars are now on sale at £5.99 plus postage (no more than £1.00).\r\n\r\nPlease look at our lastest news content to see more on calendars.\r\n\r\nThank you\r\nDawn', 'Calendar Photoshoot!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'photoshot-duke', '', '', '2014-09-28 03:11:18', '2014-09-28 02:11:18', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
