(28, 1, '2014-03-02 21:24:18', '2014-03-02 21:24:18', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="396" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]George is a 2 year old Blue male and has bags of energy. He likes a lot of fuss and does like to jump up.\r\n\r\nGeorge is currently kennelled with a bitch and is fine and happy. He has had a very short racing career.\r\n\r\nGeorge was rehomed but was brought back to us due to family illness. George is on the sponsorship scheme only at the moment as he has to settle as he is a very sensitive young man.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to sponsor George, then please contact us. George is waiting!! You can contact us or simply donate through our website.\r\n\r\nThank you so much.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'George', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'george', '', '', '2014-10-12 16:04:24', '2014-10-12 15:04:24', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=28', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
