(31, 1, '2014-03-02 21:28:41', '2014-03-02 21:28:41', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="32" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][vc_single_image image="272" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Thunder is a 5 year old Brindle male.\r\n\r\nThunder has a lovely personality; he is currently housed with a bitch that he gets on fine with. He walks very well on the lead and he does get walked regularly. He doesn’t pull or jump around at all. He is a very pleasant boy.\r\n\r\nThunder would be an addition to anyone’s settee. He is now looking for his forever home to relax and take it easy and be loved.\r\n\r\nIf you think you have what Thunder is looking for, then please contact us as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nThunder has now been rehomed &amp; can be seen opposite enjoying some quality snooze time in his new home.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Thunder', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'thunder', '', '', '2014-09-22 18:14:47', '2014-09-22 18:14:47', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=31', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
