(53, 1, '2014-03-02 22:27:45', '2014-03-02 22:27:45', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="54" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Sparkler is a lovely little black female.\r\n\r\nShe has a really friendly nature and is very loving.\r\n\r\nSparkler loves human interaction and will make a lovey pet.\r\n\r\nIf you can offer Sparkler a forever home then please contact us as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nWhen Sparkler came into the kennels she was quite shy but she has really come out of that now. She is such a beautiful girl and will really make the perfect addition to someone''s sofa!!! or bed!!!\r\n\r\nI can honestly say she is one of the sweetest greyhounds you could meet. She has a cheeky way with her too and is starting to enjoy to play. It is lovely to see.\r\n\r\nSparkler needs to be in a home where she can have the one to one attention and love she deserves.\r\n\r\nShe is adorable and just waiting to steal your heart as she has stolen ours. x[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, ask a question, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Sparkler', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sparkler', '', '', '2014-09-28 05:44:13', '2014-09-28 04:44:13', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=53', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
