(55, 1, '2014-03-02 22:34:03', '2014-03-02 22:34:03', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="56" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]I would like to introduce you to a really special young man called Vinnie.\r\n\r\nVinne is a black greyhound who has been castrated and he is an absolutely lovely boy!! He is funny, kind, loving, sweet and clean. There is nothing I can say about this young boy that is not good. He eats well, knocks 3 times to come back in when he''s been out, he is a heart stealer! He looks up at you and melts you.\r\n\r\nNow Vinnie is not without his little odd bits missing! He was attacked and had parts of his ears chewed off but this only adds to his charm. His ears do not cause him any problems and he just looks so cute. vinnie2\r\n\r\nVinnie will win anyone over and he has lived in a house and as I say, is he very clean in his kennel.\r\n\r\nHe as a few of our greyhounds, has a cheeky side to him and likes to play. He is a quiet dog all in all though as most greyhound, he loves his bed! He loves his food too and like to carry his dish on occasions!! He does love to be called ''A lovely boy'' .\r\n\r\nIf anyone feels they have what it takes to give Vinnie his forever special home, then please contact us as soon as possible. We do need to help Vinnie soon as he needs a comfy bed and sofa and TV to watch with a mum and dad who will pamper him.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Vinnie', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'vinnie', '', '', '2014-09-25 11:08:24', '2014-09-25 11:08:24', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=55', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
