(61, 1, '2014-03-02 22:53:36', '2014-03-02 22:53:36', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="62" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]This is Patch, she is a very lovable dog.\r\n\r\nShe was re-homed with a couple but unfortunately, whilst out on a walk, she was badly attacked by another dog. Patch was too traumatised to remain in a home and therefore has returned to the rescue where she will live out her life as a sponsor dog.\r\n\r\nPlease can you help by sponsoring Patch?[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="If you would like to adopt, sponsor, arrange a visit or just ask questions, please do get in touch." style="rounded" txt_align="right" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Get%20In%20Touch|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Patch', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'patch', '', '', '2014-09-28 06:18:30', '2014-09-28 05:18:30', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=61', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
