(409, 1, '2014-10-28 17:12:04', '2014-10-28 17:12:04', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="410" css_animation="left-to-right" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large" border_color="grey"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Meet Trio\r\n\r\nTrio is 4 years old and was hand reared by Karen at the rescue.\r\n\r\nHe is the most sensitive cat you will meet. He is so sweet and a very beautiful young boy.\r\n\r\nTrio always looks after you if you feel unwell and although he is quite a nervous little boy he is such a kind hearted soul.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to sponsor Trio then please contact us.\r\n\r\nHe will be your forever friend. xxx[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button call_text="If you would like to adopt, sponsor or have any questions, please do get in touch. " title="Contact Us" target="_self" color="btn-primary" icon="none" size="btn-large" position="cta_align_bottom" href="http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/get-in-touch/"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Trio', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'trio', '', '', '2014-10-28 17:12:59', '2014-10-28 17:12:59', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/?post_type=cats&#038;p=409', 0, 'cats', '', 0),
