(381, 1, '2014-10-01 17:58:44', '2014-10-01 16:58:44', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="382" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Meet Pancake - approx. 7 to 8 year old female.\r\n\r\nDue to unfortunate circumstances, Pancake is desperately looking for a forever home.\r\n\r\nHer owners are having to relocate across to America due to family reasons and thought it unfair to put Pancake through such a trauma of a long flight.\r\n\r\nThey would like Pancake to be with someone who could give her as much love as they have and she will return this love in massive bundles.\r\n\r\nShe is good with children and other dogs but not cats or smaller animals.\r\n\r\nPancake woud be ideal for an older couple or a couple looking to just spoil her rotten. Please can you help? She is very loving.\r\n\r\nPlease give Pancake thought?\r\n\r\nIf you can help then please call Dawn on 07811 296029 as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nPancake has now been re-homed[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Pancake', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'pancake', '', '', '2014-10-28 17:03:27', '2014-10-28 17:03:27', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=381', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
