(259, 3, '2014-09-22 17:46:07', '2014-09-22 17:46:07', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="258" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large" style="vc_box_shadow" border_color="grey"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Apollo is a big, strong boy who has been at the rescue some time along with his kennel mate Pandora.\r\n\r\nHe is a friendly chap but we would like Apollo and Pandora to be rehomed as a pair to someone who is very experienced with greyhounds due to their size and strength and background.\r\n\r\nThese pair are a love match and spend a lot of time cuddled up in bed together.\r\n\r\nPlease get in touch if you think you may be the right mummy or daddy for this handsome couple.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button call_text="If you would like to adopt, sponsor, arrange a visit or just have some questions, please do get in touch." title="Contact Us" target="_self" color="btn-primary" icon="none" size="btn-large" position="cta_align_bottom" href="http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/get-in-touch/"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Apollo & Pandora', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '107-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-09-22 17:46:07', '2014-09-22 17:46:07', '', 107, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/107-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
