(283, 1, '2014-10-02 13:30:35', '2014-10-02 12:30:35', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="383" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]This is Connie!\r\n\r\nConnie is a 12 year old brindle female who has been in the kennels for quite a few years.\r\n\r\nConnie is looking for a special someone to care for her and give her some quality time for her last few years.\r\n\r\nShe is an amazing girl who has been somewhat overlooked. I don''t really know why apart from she is quite shy.\r\n\r\nIf you can help in any way then please give me a call. Connie is waiting...paws crossed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThank you.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="59" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]This is lance and he was born in 2006.\r\n\r\nHe has been a racing dog and now would like to retire on to your sofa and make you a good pet and companion.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Connie', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'connie', '', '', '2014-10-02 13:30:35', '2014-10-02 12:30:35', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/2014site/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=283', 0, 'thedogs', '', 4),
(408, 1, '2014-10-28 17:03:22', '2014-10-28 17:03:22', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="382" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Meet Pancake - approx. 7 to 8 year old female.\n\nDue to unfortunate circumstances, Pancake is desperately looking for a forever home.\n\nHer owners are having to relocate across to America due to family reasons and thought it unfair to put Pancake through such a trauma of a long flight.\n\nThey would like Pancake to be with someone who could give her as much love as they have and she will return this love in massive bundles.\n\nShe is good with children and other dogs but not cats or smaller animals.\n\nPancake woud be ideal for an older couple or a couple looking to just spoil her rotten. Please can you help? She is very loving.\n\nPlease give Pancake thought?\n\nIf you can help then please call Dawn on 07811 296029 as soon as possible.\n\nThank you.\n\nPancake has now been re-homed[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Pancake', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '381-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-28 17:03:22', '2014-10-28 17:03:22', '', 381, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/381-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
