(393, 1, '2014-10-12 15:46:44', '2014-10-12 14:46:44', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="394" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]This is Freya!!!\r\n\r\nFreya is a 3 year old black female greyhound who unfortunately will never be able to be rehomed due to the trauma she suffered before she came to us.\r\n\r\nWe did try to rehome Freya once but she was so terrified that we had no choice but to bring her home here where she feels happy &amp; safe with her ''mummy '' Karen.\r\n\r\nIt is a shame that such a young dog has had to suffer so much to cause such distress that she can never have the chance to find a loving family.\r\n\r\nWe will love her here as our own and she has now become our main sponsor dog. She is a friendly little girl when anyone visits and is very cheeky. She is a delight in the kennels and enjoys her life here. It just saddens us for her as she is so loving.\r\n\r\nShe will live her life out here.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to sponsor Freya then please contact us or donate through the website. Freya would really appreciate it. We are an independent rescue and receive no funding from the racing industry although all our dogs are ex racers.\r\n\r\nThank you xxx[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Freya', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'freya', '', '', '2014-10-12 15:47:41', '2014-10-12 14:47:41', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=393', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
