(389, 1, '2014-10-03 18:38:28', '2014-10-03 17:38:28', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="390" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]This is Teddy....\r\n\r\nTeddy by name &amp; Teddy by nature!!! He is a blue boy who is 9 years old. He has been at the rescue for a number of years and due to the way in which Teddy was treated he will never be in a position to be rehomed as he is far too nervous.\r\n\r\nHe is totally happy and settled at the rescue and loves his mummy Karen so much.\r\n\r\nTeddy is a dream and a pleasure to be around. He is on the sponsorship scheme and so if you want to sponsor Teddy he will be happy to be your friend for life!!!\r\n\r\nThank you from Teddy. xxx[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Teddy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'teddy', '', '', '2014-10-04 17:57:32', '2014-10-04 16:57:32', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=389', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
