(397, 1, '2014-10-12 16:03:31', '2014-10-12 15:03:31', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="396" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]George is a 2 year old Blue male and has bags of energy. He likes a lot of fuss and does like to jump up.\n\nGeorge is currently kennelled with a bitch and is fine and happy. He has had a very short racing career.\n\nGeorge was rehomed but was brought back to us due to family illness. George is on the sponsorship scheme only at the moment as he has to settle as he is a very sensitive young man.\n\nIf you would like to sponsor George, then please contact us. George is waiting!! You can contact us or simply donate through our website.\n\nThank you so much.\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'George', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '28-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-12 16:03:31', '2014-10-12 15:03:31', '', 28, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/28-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(398, 1, '2014-10-12 16:23:39', '2014-10-12 15:23:39', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="399" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]These two lovely white &amp; black greyhounds are a boy called Lobo and a girl called Blanca!\r\n\r\nThey are brother and sister and are 7 years old.\r\n\r\nThese two are real fun loving dogs and bounce around the kennels having the time of their lives. They are real loves though and love a cuddle and are very affectionate.\r\n\r\nThey love food...and more food...and treats....and more treats!!\r\n\r\nIf you would like to sponsor Lobo or Blanca then they would be so, so excited about this!\r\n\r\nplease contact us or donate through the website on our donate button which will link you to paypal.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThank you. x[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Lobo & Blanca', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'lobo-blanca', '', '', '2014-10-12 16:23:39', '2014-10-12 15:23:39', '', 0, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/?post_type=thedogs&#038;p=398', 0, 'thedogs', '', 0),
