(401, 1, '2014-10-12 16:29:17', '2014-10-12 15:29:17', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="27" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Buster is a beautiful fawn male.\n\nHe has a big heart and loves cuddles. He loves to play and has a real friendly nature.\n\nHe enjoys his walks and never leaves your side.\n\nBuster will make a real companion.\n\nHe is a very fussy boy and loves people and although he does get on with other dogs we would say that Buster would be better off as an only dog as he does need one to one attention and needs someone who understands greyhounds as he can be a little giddy at times.\n\nHaving said this he can also be quite shy to start with and does have a lot to say for himself when the other dogs are around.\n\nHe is a very friendly boy and a big baby!\n\nWe would recommend that Buster be rehomed with no other pets and no young children.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="59" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]This is lance and he was born in 2006.\n\nHe has been a racing dog and now would like to retire on to your sofa and make you a good pet and companion.[/vc_column_text][vc_cta_button2 h2="To arrange a visit, adopt or sponsor, please do get in touch. " style="rounded" txt_align="left" title="Contact Us" btn_style="rounded" color="blue" size="md" position="bottom" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greyhoundrescue.org.uk%2F2014site%2Fget-in-touch%2F|title:Contact%20Us|"][/vc_column][/vc_row]