(471, 2, '2015-01-15 13:54:03', '2015-01-15 13:54:03', 'Please contact the rescue direct on 01205 290145 or 07811 296029 for information about adoption a greyhound.\n\nWe like to talk to out potential owners and get to know a bit about you so we can find the right family member for you and most importantly, find the right human for the greyhound!!\n\nWe do ask questions like:\n\nDo you have any other pets?\n\nWhat type of property do you live in?\n\nIs your property owned or rented?\n\nWhat is the height of your fencing? and is it all secure?\n\nDo you have children and if so what age?\n\nHave you had greyhounds before?\n\nThere is no right or wrong answer to any of these questions so please do not be put off by this. We simply like to get it right for both you and the dog. The dogs welfare is always the most important thing to us. Afterall, We must remember what these dogs have been through and how lucky these are to have made it into rescue. We need your help and support to make the right choice so that we can continue to take the next ''lucky'' one.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThank you.\n\nDawn\n\n&nbsp;', 'Adopting a Greyhound', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '151-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-15 13:54:03', '2015-01-15 13:54:03', '', 151, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/151-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
