\n<strong>Wolfie was an amazing greyhound and was at the rescue for 20 years. We will be sharing her story and pictures throughout the appeal.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Thank you.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Karen Schultz (&amp; Wolfie) X</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-01 19:01:23', '2015-02-01 19:01:23', '', 12, 'http://www.greyhoundrescue.org.uk/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
